WAFER WORKS OPTR said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 43.19% to NT$23,742,000 from NT$41,792,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales             23,742           41,792    
YOY%             -43.19%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             71,880          292,736    
YOY%             -75.45% 
=================================================================
 